videos.description: Jazz Peavy fumbles after completion which is recovered by Northwestern and leads to a Wildcats field goal.
videos.headline: Wisconsin fumbles on first offensive play

videos.description: Jonathan Taylor runs for 7 yards to give Wisconsin the lead in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Taylor dives in for Badgers' TD

videos.description: Clayton Thorson's pass is picked off by Natrell Jamerson who returns it for four yards early in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Thornson's pass intercepted by Wisconsin

videos.description: Alex Hornibrook's pass is intercepted by JR Pace for Wisconsin's second turnover of the game.
videos.headline: Hornibrook's pass is picked off

videos.description: Clayton Thorson completes to Cameron Green for a one-yard touchdown to give the Wildcats a 10-7 lead.
videos.headline: Thorson finds Green for the lead

videos.description: Alex Hornibrook's pass is picked off on the Wisconsin 31 by Godwin Igwebuike. It's Wisconsin's third turnover of the game.
videos.headline: Hornibrook throws second pick of the day

videos.description: Northwestern head coach Pat Fitzgerald discusses what the Wildcats need to do in the second half.
videos.headline: Fitzgerald: "I feel great"

videos.description: Jonathan Taylor runs for 11 yards into the end zone to put Wisconsin ahead in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Taylor's 11-yard run puts the Badgers ahead

videos.description: Alex Hornibrook connects with Quintez Cephus for 61 yards to set up Wisconsin in the red zone.
videos.headline: Hornibrook finds Cephus to put the Badgers in the red zone

videos.description: Alex Hornibrook finds Danny Davis III for a five-yard touchdown in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Davis' TD extends Wisconsin's lead

videos.description: Clayton Thorson is sacked by Garret Dooley and Natrell Jamerson for a seven-yard loss to end the third quarter.
videos.headline: Thorson sacked for the 5th time today

videos.description: Alex Hornibrook completes to A.J. Taylor for 33-yards that leads to a Wisconsin field goal.
videos.headline: Taylor puts the Badgers in the red zone

videos.description: Clayton Thorson finds Ramaud Chiaokhiao-Bowman in the end zone for a two-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Northwestern TD closes the gap

videos.description: Clayton Thorson finds Garrett Dickerson for a five-yard touchdown late in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Dickerson's TD makes it a one-score game

videos.description: Clayton Thorson is sacked by D'Cota Dixon in the end zone for a safety.
videos.headline: Wisconsin's safety secures win

videos.description: Wisconsin head coach Paul Chryst discusses the Badgers' 33-24 win over the Wildcats and  what improvements can still be made for next week.
videos.headline: Chryst: "Proud of the effort"

videos.description: No. 10 Wisconsin improves to 4-0 on the season with a 33-24 victory over Northwestern.
videos.headline: Wisconsin holds off Northwestern to remain undefeated
